title: The Cars - Westwood One  Hou. TX.(Live 2-CD) VBRak
description:
The Cars - Westwood One  Houston. TX.(Live 2-CD) VBRak

I notice a uptick in activity from the Cars here in the P2P world so I will share this show I had laying about. And I am still trying to locate the  The Cars Moving In Quadio show so If you know tell .
 I never will quit searching and eventually will find it. And then I will Post it EVERYWHERE unless there is a good reason not to. 

Anyway lets get to it...

The Summit
Houston, Texas
September 11, 1984
Promoting their fifth album "Heartbeat City"
Westwood One FM broadcast
Runtime:  84:01  (minutes/seconds)

Ben Orr: lead vocals, bass (R.I.P.)
David Robinson: drums
